Generative AI
AI at Meta
We’re excited to bring generative AI technology to our products. That’s why we’re developing AI at Meta, a collection of generative AI features and experiences in our apps, along with the models that power them. Learn more about generative AI, how we use your information for AI at Meta and the controls you have.
